@startuml ktop_py_resource_risk_view
title Resource Risk View Data Flow

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false

start
:User presses z;
:Open styled Resource Risk page;
:Read current ClusterSnapshot;
:Flatten pods to pod/container pairs;

:Find containers without CPU or memory requests;
:Find containers without CPU or memory limits;
if (Live metrics available?) then (yes)
  :Calculate usage/request ratios;
  :Calculate usage/limit ratios;
else (no)
  :Show that live usage ratios are unavailable;
endif
:Aggregate top CPU and memory by namespace;
:Aggregate top CPU and memory by workload owner;

:Render summary cards;
:Render Missing Requests / Limits,\nHigh Usage Ratios, and Top Consumers panels;
:Tab or Shift+Tab changes focused panel;
:Arrow and page keys scroll focused panel;
stop

@enduml
